ing: 1 pound skinless, boneless chicken breast, cut-up

des: "This simply delicious skillet dish features a tasty combination of cooked chicken, mixed vegetables and Campbell'sÂ® Condensed Cream of Chicken Soup, heated together and served over hot biscuits."
ins:
